{
  "stem": "23645.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I knew her name, and I knew where she was, I would certainly [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] put forward her name to Yad Vashem, to declare her a righteous Gentile.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Although both our lives were jeopardized, I didn't think of mine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't give a damn about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted her lunch, no matter what cost.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she risked her life to do this human kindness.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wish I knew where she is or who she is-- if she's still alive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, good heavens, no, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, I would risk the-- the source, jeopardize her-- her life and mine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't tell it to anyone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I also ate it secretly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And how did she know, I mean, that I would do this?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was-- you see that-- that jump and her faith in me, that I would be discreet enough to swallow this food and not jeopardize her.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But she took that chance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She took that leap of faith in me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I never-- I can see her look, her piercing look, on me, full of compassion, full of menschlichkeit, full of-- whatever she was, she was obviously a wonderful human being.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were looking at me, and-- with-- like this lady.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at work, and so on, people were kind to me, of sorts, including some of the SS men.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, it was-- after they distributed the soup, for instance, at lunchtime, when we had our break-- we had about 20 minutes to eat it-- if there was anything left over, I would get it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was very seldom left over, but sometimes there was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a little-- little something at the end of the pot.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
